data.description: Nestled in a cute cul-de-sac in Fall Creek, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem boasts comfort and is move-in-ready. The open concept living room has beautiful windows allowing for natural lighting and a gas fireplace. The living room, kitchen, laundry room, secondary bathroom, and hallway have beautiful tile flooring, creating a seamless flow throughout the home. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, pantry, island with bar seating, faux beams, and dining room. Primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom Whirlpool tub, and tiled shower. The large backyard provides ample room for entertaining, gardening, a pool, or adding a personal touch. Located close to the Turnpike, I-40, Harrah Heritage Park, schools, dining, and approx. 30 minutes to Tinker.
